---
// About Section Component
---

<section id="about" class="py-24 px-6 bg-zinc-950 border-t-2 border-cyan-500">
	<div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
		<h2 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-black text-center mb-4 tracking-tight">
			<span class="text-white">我们是谁</span>
		</h2>
		<div class="text-center mb-16">
			<span class="text-cyan-400 font-mono text-sm tracking-[0.3em]">ABOUT US</span>
		</div>

		<div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
			<!-- Card 1 -->
			<div class="group relative p-8 bg-black border-2 border-zinc-800 hover:border-cyan-500 transition-all duration-300">
				<div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-2 h-2 bg-cyan-500"></div>
				<div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-2 h-2 bg-cyan-500"></div>
				<div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-2 h-2 bg-cyan-500"></div>
				<div class="absolute bottom-0 right-0 w-2 h-2 bg-cyan-500"></div>

				<div class="w-16 h-16 mb-6 bg-cyan-500/10 border-2 border-cyan-500 flex items-center justify-center text-3xl">
					💻
				</div>
				<h3 class="text-2xl font-black text-white mb-4 tracking-tight">技术驱动</h3>
				<p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
					专注于前沿技术探索，涵盖Web开发、移动应用、AI、云计算等多个技术领域
				</p>
			</div>

			<!-- Card 2 -->
			<div class="group relative p-8 bg-black border-2 border-zinc-800 hover:border-cyan-500 transition-all duration-300">
				<div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-2 h-2 bg-cyan-500"></div>
				<div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-2 h-2 bg-cyan-500"></div>
				<div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-2 h-2 bg-cyan-500"></div>
				<div class="absolute bottom-0 right-0 w-2 h-2 bg-cyan-500"></div>

				<div class="w-16 h-16 mb-6 bg-cyan-500/10 border-2 border-cyan-500 flex items-center justify-center text-3xl">
					🚀
				</div>
				<h3 class="text-2xl font-black text-white mb-4 tracking-tight">项目实战</h3>
				<p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
					参与真实项目开发，从idea到上线全流程体验，积累宝贵的实战经验
				</p>
			</div>

			<!-- Card 3 -->
			<div class="group relative p-8 bg-black border-2 border-zinc-800 hover:border-cyan-500 transition-all duration-300">
				<div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-2 h-2 bg-cyan-500"></div>
				<div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-2 h-2 bg-cyan-500"></div>
				<div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-2 h-2 bg-cyan-500"></div>
				<div class="absolute bottom-0 right-0 w-2 h-2 bg-cyan-500"></div>

				<div class="w-16 h-16 mb-6 bg-cyan-500/10 border-2 border-cyan-500 flex items-center justify-center text-3xl">
					🤝
				</div>
				<h3 class="text-2xl font-black text-white mb-4 tracking-tight">团队协作</h3>
				<p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
					与志同道合的伙伴一起成长，在协作中提升技术能力和团队协作能力
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>
